com.google.code.ssm.api
Annotation Type ReturnDataUpdateContent

@Retention(value=RUNTIME)
@Target(value=METHOD)
public @interface ReturnDataUpdateContent

Marks method return value as an update content. This annotation should be used together with one of the Update*Cache annotations.
